<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tease-v">tease <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /tiːz/    美 /tiːz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>取笑；戏弄：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She used to <strong>tease</strong> me <strong>about</strong> my hair.
她以前经常取笑我的发型。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t take what he said seriously; he was only teasing.
别拿他的话当真，他不过是在开玩笑。</p></div></div>